{
  "stem": "802.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was very fortunate that I was put towards the very end of the barrack where people, you know, relieved themselves.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were barrels there, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Ger-- there was a German who ran the-- who was the-- the-- the commandant of the-- actually, he was-- he was a German national.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when they came out to weed us out, you know, to take us, there was no-- there were no gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were mass-- there was a mass grave.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when they came to weed us out of there, [BACKGROUND NOISE] they never went far enough to find me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that saved my life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Ironically enough, that saved my life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then ultimately I left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we'd learned that there were two cousins in that concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we were sent to another concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And incidentally, my life was saved because one day my sister poured out a can of urine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, the lavatories were very, very far, and it was bitter cold.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't have any clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What I was wearing at the time was a housecoat, a huge flannel housecoat that was full of blood of menses of a woman, the period of the woman, in the back.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course we couldn't wash it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My hair was shaved, so I was-- I didn't get a scarf, but I got a bolero, a very heavy rayon bolero.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we used to tie it in the front, you may have seen, and make a knot here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And once somebody said, who's that devil with the knot on her head?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I just didn't look human.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one-- oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we ate from these [POLISH], we used to call it, from these cans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
